name: simplix-react
description: Package-first React framework that derives a type-safe client, React Query hooks, TanStack Form hooks, and MSW mocks from one Zod/OpenAPI contract per domain. Enforces framework-first derivation, package/module (FSD) separation, and CLI + OpenAPI scaffolding over hand-rolled code.
version: 1.1.0
entry: simplix-react/SKILL.md
references:
  - simplix-react/references/cli-workflow.md
  - simplix-react/references/api-patterns.md
  - simplix-react/references/recipes.md
  - simplix-react/references/configuration.md
install: claude skill add https://raw.githubusercontent.com/simplix-react/simplix-react/main/skills/simplix-react.skill
